dct_description_sm: Shows municipal boundaries developed between 1852 to 1917.
Shows also part of Contra Costa Co., including Richmond and El Cerrito.
Base map titled "San Francisco-Oakland terminal railways system map showing lines and cross streets, April 6th, 1916."
